high_descs: Turn left, walk forward until across from the end of the white table, turn right, walk to the table.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Turn left, walk to counter, turn right, go to microwave.
Put apple in microwave and heat it.
Take apple out of microwave, turn left, walk to sink, turn right to face sink.
anns.task_desc: Put heated apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the white table to your right.
Grab the apple on the table.
Turn left and walk to the microwave to your right.
Place the apple next to the potato inside the microwave, heat it and remove it.
Turn around and walk to the sink to your right.
Place the warm apple in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn forward and left up to the white table
Pick up the red apple from the white table
Turn left and walk to the microwave just left of the fridge
Heat the apple in the microwave then remove it
Turn left and walk to the sink
Put the apple in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple in the sink
